      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nEnrollment funnel from SRG file receipt through FIS reconciliation. Sourced from **`reporting.fact_enrollments`**.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|--------|--------|--------|\n| Correlation ID | `fact_enrollments.correlation_id` | UUID linking all records from one SRG file |\n| SRG File Type | `fact_enrollments.srg_file_type` | SRG310=New enrollment, SRG315=Update, SRG320=Termination |\n| FIS Record Type | `fact_enrollments.fis_record_type` | RT30=New account, RT37=Card update, RT60=Fund load |\n| Processing Status | `fact_enrollments.processing_status` | STAGED=in pipeline, ACCEPTED=FIS accepted, FAILED=error |\n| Records | Count of enrollment rows per batch | One row per member per file |\n\n**Pipeline flow:** SRG file arrives \u2192 Stage 1 (arrival) \u2192 Stage 2 (validate) \u2192 Stage 3 (row processing \u2192 STAGED) \u2192 Stage 4 (batch assembly) \u2192 Stage 5 (SCP egress) \u2192 Stage 6 (wait for return) \u2192 Stage 7 (reconcile \u2192 ACCEPTED/FAILED)",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
